21
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,320
Leave!

22
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:33,640
Cursed jinx.

23
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:35,040
Back to your city!

24
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,480
You are not welcome here!

25
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:39,760
Mom.

26
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:41,580
Is that what you think as well?

27
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,390
She carries the ill fate
of the solidarity star.

28
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,920
She is a bad omen

29
