from becoming a mother?

44
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:19,600
You're getting ahead of yourself.

45
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:20,640
Listen closely.

46
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,440
I decided to stay.

47
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,520
There's no way I'm leaving.

48
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,360
Fine.

49
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:28,960
Don't hurt her!

50
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,720
I'm warning you.

51
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,960
You must leave today!

52
00:03:31,220 --> 00:03:32,590
I don't care what excuses you have!

53
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:34,520
Lian, Aunt!

54
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,500
- I'm going nowhere!
- Calm down.

55
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,280
Calm down.

56
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,040
- Mom.
- Aunt.

57
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:39,890
Do you know why Li Xiaolian
doesn't want me to have a child?

58
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,640
If I ever have a child,

59
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,240
she won't inherit a thing.

60
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:43,990
Why you...

61
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,760
Slandering won't work on us.

62
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,500
As long as she's here,

63
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,080
we won't live to spend

64
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,080
a penny of the will!

65
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,720
I'd love to see what you can do to me

66
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:58,760
if I refuse

67
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,680
to leave this home.

68
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,480
You asked for this.

69
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,750
See for yourselves.

70
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,880
My goodness, Lian.

71
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,400
You were behind this!

72
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:21,200
Listen up.

73
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,840
Lin Cuihua has been criticized

74
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:24,980
by the authority for spreading
superstitious beliefs.

75
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:25,520
What?

76
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,160
The fortune teller got arrested?

77
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,960
The solidarity star is born.

78
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:33,320
Calamity will befall us.

79
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:34,520
Is that so?

80
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:35,920
Hold on.

81
00:04:39,450 --> 00:04:40,120
I can see it now.

82
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,040
You've been a fraud.

83
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,360
You will be sent to jail today.

84
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,000
Lin Cuihua.

85
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:50,600
We received reports
you're spreading superstitious beliefs.

86
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,600
Come with us.

87
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,490
Blame yourselves for being so foolish.

88
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:56,960
Lian!

89
00:04:57,220 --> 00:04:58,800
You alienated me and my daughter-in-law!

90
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,840
- I'll make you pay!
- Let go of me!

91
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:00,560
- Aunt!
- Mom!

92
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,560
You are no better.

93
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:04,360
You kicked me out
without telling Gu Dequan.

94
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,200
I'm not afraid.

95
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:08,240
I am the owner of this house.

96
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:11,280
I can decide whether or not
you should be kicked out.

97
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,040
The owner?

98
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,600
You're just a babysitter.

99
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:14,440
Why you...

100
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,640
Listen up.

101
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:17,080
He wants to make me pay,

102
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:18,360
not you.

103
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,160
Relay a message for me.

104
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:24,880
I will never

105
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,640
have a child.

106
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,760
But whatever you took from my mother,

107
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,600
