115
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:05,960
Mom.

116
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,160
The doctor said

117
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,160
I'd never

118
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:10,160
have a child in this life.

119
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,360
Fine.

120
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,640
I will arrange it.

121
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:24,320
How is the investigation?

122
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:32,000
There's another matter.

123
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,920
I suspect Chun and Li Xiaolian

124
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,720
are working together.

125
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,400
(Did you see it?)

126
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,040
(Yeah.)

127
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,720
(I saw Chun taking the ghost doll
Li Xiaolian dropped.)

128
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,360
I see.

129
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,040
Chun lives with Mom.

130
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,520
It's easy to use a haunting as a ruse.

131
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,920
Do not tell her about this.

132
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,800
I'll test her reactions.

133
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,480
Sure.

134
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:03,440
Now you know

135
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:04,920
